IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ITERATIVE-TESTS.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-ASSERT-TOTAL    PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-PASSED   PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-FAILED   PIC 9(03) VALUE 0.
01 WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED PIC S9(9).
01 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL   PIC S9(9).
01 WS-ASSERT-NAME     PIC X(40).
01 WS-P1              PIC S9(9).
01 WS-P2              PIC S9(9).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
    DISPLAY "--- ITERATIVE tests ---"
    DISPLAY " "

    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 0 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "sum_ite(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "SUM-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 3 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 6 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "sum_ite(3)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "SUM-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "factorial_ite(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FACTORIAL-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 4 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 24 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "factorial_ite(4)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FACTORIAL-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 0 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 0 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_ite(0)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 1 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_ite(1)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 6 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "fibonacci_ite(6)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "FIBONACCI-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 12 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 4 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "gcd_ite(12, 8)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "GCD-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 7 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 5 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 1 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "gcd_ite(7, 5)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "GCD-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 4 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 6 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 12 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "lcm_ite(4, 6)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "LCM-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    MOVE 6 TO WS-P1
    MOVE 8 TO WS-P2
    MOVE 24 TO WS-ASSERT-EXPECTED
    MOVE "lcm_ite(6, 8)" TO WS-ASSERT-NAME
    CALL "LCM-ITE" USING WS-P1 WS-P2 WS-ASSERT-ACTUAL
    PERFORM ASSERT-EQUAL

    PERFORM ASSERT-REPORT
    GOBACK.

COPY ASSERTS.

END PROGRAM ITERATIVE-TESTS.
